Description . Wing length 2.6–2.9 mm, similar to
C. falcatus
except as follows:

Hind femur bow-legged, with 1 preapical dorsal seta. Hind tibia bent and slightly twisted, compressed near midlength (
Fig. 90
); shorter than femur, apex dilated, bearing posteroapical comb; pv surface lacking setae. Hind tarsomeres shorter than tibia, slender.
